  slotted PHP. Ref bug 363825

  15 Oct 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  pecl-drizzle-0.4.2.ebuild:
  Simplify dependencies (changed versioning scheme).

  06 Sep 2010; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org>
  pecl-drizzle-0.4.2.ebuild:
